Generate Token
post
https://pluraluat.v2.pinepg.in/api/auth/v1/token

Use this API to generate a access token.

📘
Note:

This API is authenticated using the client secret provided in the API request.

Body Params
client_id
string
required
Unique client identifier in the Pine Labs Online database.

Example: a17ce30e-f88e-4f81-ada1-c3b4909ed232

Note: The Onboarding team has provided you with this information as part of the onboarding process.

client_secret
string
required
Unique client secret key provided while onboarding.

Example: fgwei7egyhuggwp39w8rh

Note: The Onboarding team has provided you with this information as part of the onboarding process.

grant_type
string
required
The grant type to generate a access token.

Accepted value: client_credentials

Headers
Content-Type
string
The type of content included in the HTTP message body.

Possible value: application/json.

Request-Timestamp
string
Use ISO 8601 UTC Timestamp, to create a timestamp when the generate token is requested.

Example: 2024-07-09T07:57:08.022Z

Request-ID
string
Use a global unique identifier [GUID] for the request.

Minimum: 1 characters.
Maximum: 50 characters
Example: c17ce30f-f88e-4f81-ada1-c3b4909ed235
